data.title: President George Bush and Japanese Prime Minister Kiichi Miyazawa walk together to Marine One on the White House lawn, July 1, 1992, to travel to Camp David. The two met for an hour in the Oval Office
data.meta_description: Download this stock image: President George Bush and Japanese Prime Minister Kiichi Miyazawa walk together to Marine One on the White House lawn, July 1, 1992, to travel to Camp David. The two met for an hour in the Oval Office, discussing trade issues, before traveling to Camp David for dinner. (AP Photo/Wilfredo Lee) - 2NF8GMA from Alamy's library of millions of high resolution stock photos, illustrations and vectors.
